OL,6,FSimon Scheeres, Cancer Research UK's
OL,7,Fpublic affairs manager in Wales, has
OL,8,Fsaid: "Where you live shouldn't
OL,9,Fincrease your risk of dying from this
OL,10,Fdevastating disease."
OL,12,F"Smoking remains the leading cause of
OL,13,Flung cancer, a disease that's often
OL,14,Fdiagnosed late when treatment options
OL,15,Fare more limited.
OL,17,F"One of the ways we can prevent lung
OL,18,Fcancer is to deter people from ever
OL,19,Ftaking up smoking in the first place."
