OL,4,Cdeprived areas
OL,6,FA targeted lung screening programme is
OL,7,Fbeing introduced in England however it
OL,8,Fhas yet to be introduced in Wales.
OL,10,FIt is estimated that if lung screening
OL,11,Fwas rolled out in Wales, around 240
OL,12,Fextra cases in Wales could be
OL,13,Fdiagnosed at an early stage each year.
OL,15,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"We are working across government to
OL,17,Faddress health inequalities and
OL,18,Fimprove cancer services and survival
OL,19,Frates.
