OL,6,F"We recognise the link between levels
OL,7,Fof deprivation and health outcomes,
OL,8,Fand are investing in programmes to
OL,9,Fhelp families to live healthier, more
OL,10,Factive lives.
OL,12,F"We have already introduced measures
OL,13,Ffor Wales to be smoke-free by 2030,
OL,14,Fincluding introducing smoking
OL,15,Frestrictions in playgrounds, school
OL,16,Fand hospital grounds and strengthening
OL,17,Fservices to support more people to
OL,18,Fquit smoking.
